* Gain cards (to discard pile)
* Gain an addtional action
* Gain money
* Gain an additional buy

* Reveal cards from deck
* Draw cards from deck to hands
* Add specific cards from deck to hands

* Discard cards from hand
* Discard cards from deck

* Trash cards

* Combination: multiple kinds of actions in one card


** Reaction: A player under attack can use this card to negate the attack (automatically?)